did.abstract: This collection contains bound ledger books from Teamsters Local Unions 14, 366, 572, 606, 686, 700, and 864; earlier Teamsters ledgers collectively list multiple rather than individual Local Unions. Included are cash books, day books, dues books, minutes books, expense books, membership directories, and welfare books. The ledgers date from 1903-1973, with the bulk dating from 1930-1960.

arrangement.head: Arrangement
arrangement.p: This collection is arranged numerically by Local Union, then alphabetically according to specific type of ledger. Bulk of materials are organized by a specific Local Union, except for earliest dated ledgers consisting of collective rather than individual union records.

prefercite.head: Preferred Citation
prefercite.p: Please cite unpublished materials in the following way:
Please provide the title and date of item, catalog number (if applicable it will be found written on the folder), name of the collection, name of the repository, and location of the repository.

Example: James Oglethorpe to the Trustees, 13 January 1876, RG0001 Series 1, Box 4, Folder 3. Records of the Board of Trustees, Special Collections Research Center, Gelman Library, The George Washington University, Washington, D.C.

accessrestrict.head: Conditions Governing Access
accessrestrict.p: This collection is open for research.

scopecontent.head: Scope and Contents
scopecontent.p: This collection contains bound ledger books from a variety of Teamsters Local Unions Included are cash books, day books, dues books, minutes books, expense books, membership directories, and welfare books. The ledgers date from 1891-1973, with the bulk dating from 1930-1960.
